11.25.19  11:42 pm   In the H3 podcast, you mentioned that you couldn't get out of bed because you were working so hard on hotwig. Have you experienced something similar in your current expedition?

     no

      Do you have any tips on how to overcome these moments? 

     whenever i'm feeling scared and confused, i absolutely must talk and discuss it, using language. that's the best way i deal with it. i often recommend this to others, because it works so incredibly well for me. but i'm not actually sure if this works for everyone. i know it works for some people. and those people say 'thanks bill, that helps' while the other people say 'nope, doesn't work, what else can you suggest'
